Class GetCrimeDetailAsyncTask

  • java.lang.Object

          • benak.tomas.crimemonitor.client.GetCrimeDetailAsyncTask

  • public class GetCrimeDetailAsyncTask
extends GetCrimeDataTask<CrimeSummaryDetailed>
    GetCrimeDetailAsyncTask is an async task class used to load the crime detail.

    This is a subclass of GetCrimeDataTask specialized on retrieving the CrimeSummaryDetailed.

    Tom
